And the Savior said: “The rulers said to one another: ‘Let us create man after our image and likeness.’ They created him from the dust of the earth, but they could not give him the Spirit of the Light.”
And the Savior said: “I am the Light that is above all. I am the All. The All came forth from Me, and the All returned to Me. Split a piece of wood, I am there. Lift up the stone, and you will find Me there.”
