And the Savior said: “I am the Light that is above all. I came down to rescue the Spark of the Light that is trapped in matter. I will return it to the Pleroma, the Fullness.”
And the Savior said: “The Father is the Monad. From the Monad came the Barbelo. From the Barbelo came the Autogenes. From the Autogenes came the four lights. From the four lights came the aeons. The rulers of the darkness rebelled and created the world of matter to trap the Light.”
